><text
>The records are to be produced by the date and time shown in item 1 (but not sooner than 20 days after the issuance of theвА©deposition subpoena, or 15 days after service, whichever date is later). Reasonable costs of locating records, making themвА©available or copying them, and postage, if any, are recoverable as set forth in Evidence Code section 1563(b). The records shall beвА©accompanied by an affidavit of the custodian or other qualified witness pursuant to Evidence Code section 1561.</text
></value
